    <h1>Javascript Strings</h1>
    <h2>The indexOf() Method</h2>
    <p>indexOf() method returns the position of the first occurence of a string in a string.</p>
    <p>The position of the first occurence of "locate" is:</p>
    <p id="demo"></p>
  </body>
  <script>
    let text = "Please locate where 'locate' occurs!";
    let index = text.indexOf("locate");
    document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = index;
  </script>
